db.random.weapons.melee

Class OneHandAxes

  • java.lang.Object
    • db.random.weapons.melee.OneHandAxes

  • public class OneHandAxes
extends java.lang.Object
    A Class, that stores all Onehanded Axes with MultiBonus. They can be accessed by calling getList().
